Package: ggts
Title: Easy time series visualization
Version: 0.0.1.9000
Authors@R: person("Chandler", "Lutz", email = "cl.eco@cbs.dk", role = c("aut", "cre"))
Description: This package provides easy time series visualization via ggplot2.
    The ggts package plots ts, zoo, and xts objects; implements cycles (bear market,
    recession, or other shading); and allows for standard or faceted plots.
License: GPL-2
Encoding: UTF-8
LazyData: true
Depends:
    R (>= 3.1.0),
    ggplot2 (>= 2.1.0)
Imports:
    AER,
    dplyr,
    tidyr,
    cowplot,
    xts,
    zoo
RoxygenNote: 5.0.1
Suggests: testthat

